</sense>
<sense n=""3""><number>3</number><trans>. </trans>
</sense></hom>
<hom role=""n""><pos>n</pos>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number><trans> <tr>slap</tr>. </trans>
</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> a k.o. <tr>sorcery</tr> whereby a sorcerer inflicts harm by tapping the victim. The victim counteracts the sorcery by tapping the sorcerer back. </trans>
</sense>
<sense n=""3""><number>3</number><trans> application <pb n=""190""/>for skin diseases consisting of herbs cooked in banana leaves over live coals. The cause of the disease is thought to appear in the compress after it has been applied. </trans>
