<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""0""> <itype>[B]</itype><trans> be, become dark. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Midagtum ang íyang nawung pagkadungug sa nutisya, pagbinulad,</i><trans> His face became gloomy when he heard the news; his face got tanned dark from being in the sun. </trans></eg>
