<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> for the voice to get <tr>off pitch</tr>. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Nadalag (midalag) ang íyang tíngug tungud sa hilabihang kahadluk,</i><trans> She was so frightened her voice went out of key. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""3""><number>3</number> <itype>[A1]</itype><trans> <tr>wear</tr> s.t. yellow. </trans>
</sense></hom>
