<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number> <itype>[A2; b]</itype><trans> <tr>reach</tr>, <tr>arrive</tr> at a place. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Midángat mi sa ámung distínu,</i><trans> We arrived at our destination. </trans></eg>
