<sense n=""2""><number>2</number> <itype>[A23; b5]</itype><trans> happen to s.o. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ayaw giyud ku basúla kun may mudángat nímu,</i><trans> Don’t ever blame me if s.t. happens to you. </trans></eg>
