<sense n=""2""><number>2</number> <itype>[a3]</itype><trans> be bathed in sweat, blood, etc. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Nadígù siya sa singut,</i><trans> He is bathed in sweat. </trans></eg>
