<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Ang simintu nga gíkan sa Danaw dihádu karun,</i><trans> Danao-produced cement is not popular now. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""3""><number>3</number><trans> guitar accompaniment to extemporaneous folk songs, sung in a set pattern, where beats are left out at the points where the words don’t fit the music exactly. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Dihádung dúyug nga gawía ug magbalítaw,</i><trans> Use a free accompaniment for the <ix>balítaw</ix>. </trans></eg>
</sense></hom>
<hom role=""v""><pos>v</pos>
