<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Idirikta nà siya sa util,</i><trans> Take her directly to a hotel. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""3""><number>3</number> <itype>[A; c]</itype><trans> direct s.o. s.w. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Kinsay nagdirikta ninyu nganhi?</i><trans> Who directed you here? </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""3a""><number>3a</number> <itype>[A; b]</itype><trans> direct traffic. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Gidiriktahan sa mga buy iskawut ang trápik,</i><trans> The boy scouts directed the traffic. </trans></eg>
