</sense></hom></entry>
<entry><form id=""diriyut_dariyut_subjunctive_verb"" lang=""ceb"">diriyut, dariyut <r>[<ix>subjunctive verb</ix>]</r></form>
<hom>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number><trans> [so-and-so] almost happened. </trans>
