</sense>
<sense n=""1""><number>1</number><trans> get dark, gloomy. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Buklása ang hinayhay kay nadulum na ang lángit,</i><trans> Bring the wash in because it has gotten overcast. </trans></eg>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Nadulman mi sa dálan,</i><trans> Darkness overtook us on the way. </trans></eg>
</sense>
<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> for the eyesight to fail. </trans>
</sense>
<sense n=""3""><number>3</number> <form id=""dulum_ang_pangixsip_hunaqhuxnaq"" lang=""ceb""><abbr expan=""dulum"" type=""lemma"">—</abbr> ang pangísip, hunàhúnà</form><trans> get to be blind with rage, sorrow. </trans>
