<sense n=""2""><number>2</number><trans> <tr>endorse</tr>, pass papers forward to a superior for approval. </trans>
<eg><i lang=""ceb"">Wà pa idusù ang ákung apuwintmin ngadtu sa supirbaysur,</i><trans> My appointment hasn’t been endorsed to the supervisor yet. </trans></eg>
